            "tag": "MAJESTIC PEAKS",
            "heading": "Cangshan Above the Clouds",
            "description": "Discover the mountain backbone of Dali through misty peaks, forest trails, hidden temples, and panoramic cable car views. Cangshan is where dramatic alpine scenery meets ancient legend, making it one of the most iconic natural landmarks in western Yunnan.",
            "button_label": "READ THE GUIDE",
