            "tag": "AZURE REFLECTION",
            "heading": "Erhai Lake Slow Horizons",
            "description": "Erhai is the visual soul of Dali: a vast alpine lake framed by sky, villages, and the distant line of Cangshan. From cycling routes and sunrise piers to quiet bays and sunset viewpoints, it is the place where Dali’s calmest rhythm reveals itself.",
            "button_label": "READ THE GUIDE",
