            "tag": "ARCHITECTURAL SOUL",
            "heading": "Xizhou & Bai Heritage",
            "description": "Step into one of Dali’s most culturally rich towns, where Bai courtyard architecture, indigo craft traditions, local flavors, and rice-field scenery create a living portrait of heritage. Xizhou is not only beautiful to see, but deeply rooted in everyday life.",
